  fat: 48 g
  saturated fat: 21 g
  carbohydrates: 45 g
  sugar: 16 g
  protein: 34 g
  fiber: 6 g
  sodium: 960 mg
servings: 2
author: HelloFresh
time required: 25m
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/rosemary-steak-and-creamy-dijon-sauce-686e0235249cc147aea828fe
